name: Camp Jupiter
description:
Camp Jupiter is a fictional place near the San Francisco Bay Area from the world of "The Heroes of Olympus" by Rick Riordan. It is a camp where demigod children and descendants of the Roman gods train to defend themselves from Ancient Hellenistic mythological monsters.

Connected to another piece of banner art at (575, -511) for Camp Jupiter's Greek-demigod alternate: Camp Half-Blood.
